{"tid":906573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同行證實Taylor Swift藏身行李箱「代步」　避狗仔隊跟蹤","createTime":"2018-11-18T06:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T09:48:31.000Z","uid":212399,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3955b37ec2e69048f3d9bf08cbe07093692eb928","tid":906573,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"18個月前有傳聞指出，美國女歌星Taylor Swift躲在行李箱內並以此「代步」。曾為英國組合One Direction成員之一的Zayn Malik在接受英國版《Vogue》訪問時，似乎已證實有關傳言。<br />\n<br />\nZayn Malik指出，Taylor Swift自2017年開始便有這個做法，她以這樣的方式躲避令人討厭的記者。至於Taylor Swift的公關人員則未有回覆媒體的查詢。<br />\n有關傳聞始於2017年7月。供應明星及名人照片的Splash News圖片社有一張相引起外界注意，照片中兩名「大隻佬」在Taylor Swift家門外搬動一個行李箱。它附有耐人尋味的圖片說明：「Taylor Swift被人用行李箱運送，（箱子）從她位於特里貝卡（Tribeca）的家運到其貨車上。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2106513/org/b324b8d8613c5f2e0adad245a280383f.PNG/45DF3SPit2dJN71Tp1CYc_pkSLXMP5A966mdruupna4?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2106513%2Forg%2Fb324b8d8613c5f2e0adad245a280383f.PNG%2F45DF3SPit2dJN71Tp1CYc_pkSLXMP5A966mdruupna4%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=97cd9b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明星名人通訊社Splash News於2017年發布一張照片，圖片說明指Taylor Swift躲在行李箱內，並被人運上貨車。不少人最初覺得這樣很荒謬，但當聯想到Taylor Swift一向不喜被記者「跟出跟入」，也覺得不無可能。<br />\n相中顯示從她家中搬出一個行李箱也相當「大陣仗」。目擊者指有兩輛凱迪拉克（Cadillac）汽車、三部多用途運動車以及十多名保安人員抵達Taylor Swift家，然後將一個行李箱搬離她的香閨。那個黑色箱子大得需要兩名成年人才搬得動。有關她藏身其中的揣測也隨之廣為網民討論。Taylor Swift身高5呎8吋，倘若這「專屬交通公具」是真有其事，也要相若的空間才能讓她容身。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2106515/org/619403f3fbabf3806da5d0923d3f6890.jpg/6-09xFKnIGqUZi9SpC2OIuLJdNDCnw6sOM31nDjN9Zw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2106515%2Forg%2F619403f3fbabf3806da5d0923d3f6890.jpg%2F6-09xFKnIGqUZi9SpC2OIuLJdNDCnw6sOM31nDjN9Zw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=46f50218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTaylor Swift曾與英國影星赫度斯頓（Tom Hiddleston）相戀。兩人後來分手，她到美國曼哈頓待了數月，其間沒人知道她的行蹤。圖為兩人於2016年7月27日現身街頭。<br />\n照片最後在公司跟這位女歌手的工作隊伍談話後撤回，原因是照片無法證明她在箱子內。<br />\nTaylor Swift的行蹤之所以為引起外界興趣，是因為她在與英國男星湯赫度斯頓（Tom Hiddleston）分手後，曾待在美國曼哈頓數月，期間完全無人知道這位女星也在此地。<br />\n英國《都市報》報道，她也曾公開承認自己有「偷龍轉鳳」的方法去擺脫「狗仔隊」。"},{"pid":"a1b4f1d9fb5c0a6c34d31796179573a40718f83a","tid":906573,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9b72fc6042436182031a5f7ca6aeac190d6916","tid":906573,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"都真係好撚慘，請替身同喬裝好難咩"},{"pid":"279ecfaf9b9f2542738c8a0e9b3e4ca972d3a307","tid":906573,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"淫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a2ef9049354592225d54e1444ce4c7f20924a3","tid":906573,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好淫<br />\n好似av d玩具咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d04692628ef166a8d31c9db973105f1a55b15f","tid":906573,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c624aafc3c159f36ad66fffdfcbf3afc45e9f4","tid":906573,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"箱入之女"},{"pid":"58c40a579a8d665ebeeb23dbe774ec4e7620f27b","tid":906573,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"Taylor Swift身高5呎8吋???<br />\n 點止呀?分分鐘六呎都有WO佢<br />\n利申:成日J佢"},{"pid":"da981e48471164d89d02e5f9b6bff7c847d6f854","tid":906573,"uid":137569,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3955b37ec2e69048f3d9bf08cbe07093692eb928","tid":906573,"uid":212399,"like":0,"di